real-world problems. For many applications, real numbers suffice; that is, real numbers with the
appropriate units attached can be used to answer questions like вҖңHow close is the nearest Sasquatch
nest?вҖқ There are other times though, when these kinds of quantities do not suffice. Perhaps it is
important to know, for instance, how close the nearest Sasquatch nest is as well as the direction in
